<A>__{she stands on the precipice of being transported away from the logic which has been her lifeline.}
<C>__{melvin}
<D>__{i think most people miss that about you and i watch wondering how they can watch you bring them food and clear their dishes and never get that they have just met the greatest woman alive... and the fact that i get it makes me feel great... about me!}
<P>__{(a real question}
<D>__{filled with}
