<C>__{melvin}
<D>__{i know i can do better.}
<A>__{they embrace again. he does indeed do much better. a first class smooch. camera moves down to see his foot land squarely on a crack in the sidewalk without his knowledge. they break look at each other without a notion of where to take it from here, and the almost in unison begin to walk away from camera, melvin following a path that avoids cracks. suddenly the lights of the bakery turn on as it opens for business.}
